            "ignore": false,
            "order": 4,
            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": "Assuming that equality holds for Eq.  $(6)$  and combining it with Eq. (3), we can obtain  $I^{(1)}, \\ldots, I^{(N)}$  as",
            "line_with_spans": [
                {
                    "category_type": "text_span",
