                1430
            ],
            "ignore": false,
            "order": 10,
            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": "Interestingly, this type of quasi-equivalence does not hold for joint aperture-exposure coding. By using Eq. (1), the imaging process of Eq. (2) is rewritten as",
            "line_with_spans": [
                {
                    "category_type": "text_span",
                    "poly": [
