                2748
            ],
            "ignore": false,
            "order": 16,
            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": "Our algorithm consists of two parts: AcqNet and Rec-Net. AcqNet describes the data-acquisition process using a coded aperture and an event camera as",
            "line_with_spans": [
                {
                    "category_type": "text_span",
                    "poly": [
                        202,
                        2608,
                        1190,
                        2608,
                        1190,
